name: Lieutenant Grond
Lore: 'Colonel Dyer''s aide. Coordinates scout actions. As a youth, raced swoops on homeworld of Corellia. Formerly served with Emperor''s Demonstration Team.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots or any swoop he drives. When in battle at an exterior site, adds 2 to attrition against opponent for each of your biker scout/trooper (non-biker scout) pairs present.',
